- No, she's not.

01:24:12.640 --> 01:24:13.880
Get in the car.

01:24:15.640 --> 01:24:17.642
Well, I don't feel like getting
in the car with you and her.

01:24:21.840 --> 01:24:23.842
Do you know what I've
been doing all night?

01:24:25.000 --> 01:24:26.800
I'll find another ride.

01:24:26.880 --> 01:24:28.006
Hey. Hey, get in the car.

01:24:28.240 --> 01:24:29.241
Stop!

01:24:29.440 --> 01:24:30.960
