01:24:31.040 --> 01:24:32.769
- Let go of me!
- You think I like this?

01:24:32.880 --> 01:24:33.927
Where were you?

01:24:35.360 --> 01:24:36.930
You can't pick up your phone even once?

01:24:37.120 --> 01:24:39.920
