about me just because people are watching.

01:24:40.000 --> 01:24:41.160
Oh, give me a break.

01:24:41.240 --> 01:24:42.320
Oh, face it.

01:24:42.400 --> 01:24:44.920
You can't wait to take me home
so you can be Mom's little hero.

01:24:45.000 --> 01:24:46.923
You live for that shit.

01:25:01.680 --> 01:25:02.841
KRISTA: Just let it go.

01:25:04.480 --> 01:25:05.925
Darian.

01:25:06.160 --> 01:25:08.367
Darian?

01:25:11.840 --> 01:25:13.205
Hey, I just want you to know
you're right, Nadine.

01:25:13.320 --> 01:25:15.527
- Darian, we don't need to do this...
- You're right about everything!

01:25:20.040 --> 01:25:22.120
I don't give a shit about you.

01:25:22.200 --> 01:25:26.649
I'm only here for me,
and my life is fuckin' incredible.

01:25:27.360 --> 01:25:28.441
I love it.

01:25:31.240 --> 01:25:33.880
No, I love spending another night
talking Mom off the ledge.

01:25:33.960 --> 01:25:35.640
I love only applying to schools nearby

01:25:35.720 --> 01:25:38.440
because who knows what'll happen
in the house if I'm not around to fix it?

01:25:38.520 --> 01:25:42.490
And I love that the one person
who makes me feel

01:25:42.600 --> 01:25:44.204
like I could take a fuckin' breath,

01:25:48.960 --> 01:25:51.725
I can't have without
completely destroying you.

01:25:53.600 --> 01:25:55.090
So, you're right.

01:25:56.120 --> 01:25:58.248
You're right. It's a blast.

01:25:58.920 --> 01:26:00.081
I win.

01:26:07.920 --> 01:26:09.968
Hey, can you give her a ride home, please?

01:26:11.080 --> 01:26:12.161
Thanks.

01:26:44.800 --> 01:26:45.801
(SIGHS)

01:26:55.320 --> 01:26:57.448
Look, I'm not very good
at this kind of thing. Uh...

01:26:59.720 --> 01:27:03.441
But I think we both know
what needs to be said right now,

01:27:04.960 --> 01:27:06.962
so I'm just gonna come
right out and say it.

01:27:10.480 --> 01:27:11.845
Get out of the car.

01:27:12.960 --> 01:27:13.961
(CHUCKLES)

01:27:17.960 --> 01:27:19.689
(SIGHS)

01:27:22.200 --> 01:27:24.168
