- See you Monday.

01:28:20.240 --> 01:28:21.446
Hey.

01:28:32.080 --> 01:28:35.402
Look, I just wanted to say that

01:28:38.240 --> 01:28:41.483
I'm sorry for being a bitch tonight.

01:28:44.480 --> 01:28:47.086
For the past couple weeks.

01:28:49.280 --> 01:28:51.408
And the past 17 years before that.

01:28:55.080 --> 01:28:57.280
I know this isn't any easier for you.

01:28:57.360 --> 01:28:58.521
I know that.

01:28:59.960 --> 01:29:02.361
I think some deranged
part of me likes thinking

01:29:02.480 --> 01:29:05.006
I'm the only one with real problems.

01:29:05.440 --> 01:29:08.330
Like that makes me special.

01:29:13.200 --> 01:29:17.442
You know, ever since we were little,
I would get this feeling like...

01:29:19.640 --> 01:29:23.770
Like I'm floating outside of my body,
looking down on myself.

01:29:26.000 --> 01:29:28.367
And I hate what I see.

01:29:30.080 --> 01:29:33.801
How I'm acting, the way I sound.

01:29:36.440 --> 01:29:38.920
And I don't know how to change it.

01:29:40.440 --> 01:29:42.727
And I'm so scared

01:29:43.800 --> 01:29:46.724
that that feeling is never gonna go away.

01:29:53.840 --> 01:29:55.569
I'm sorry.

01:29:57.200 --> 01:29:58.531
Really.

01:30:00.640 --> 01:30:02.005
Good night.

01:30:05.040 --> 01:30:06.121
Hey, Nadine.

01:30:50.720 --> 01:30:52.688
- Good night.
- Good night.

01:31:17.720 --> 01:31:19.768
- Hey.
- Hey.

01:31:20.800 --> 01:31:21.961
