01:31:40.640 --> 01:31:41.801
Have a great day.

01:31:42.280 --> 01:31:43.645
Thank you.

01:31:44.560 --> 01:31:45.561
Um...

01:31:47.600 --> 01:31:49.045
Can I call you later?

01:31:50.040 --> 01:31:51.246
Okay.

01:31:54.880 --> 01:31:56.600
- That was good.
- Mmm-hmm.

01:31:56.680 --> 01:31:58.640
- Right?
- That was so good.

01:31:58.720 --> 01:32:00.085
I miss her.

01:32:28.840 --> 01:32:30.171
Nadine?

01:32:37.640 --> 01:32:40.803
Sit back, relax,
